faqDataList.faqTitle: How Can I Earn Money Trading Forex?
faqDataList.faqDesc: You earn money in Forex due to the difference in exchange rates. The trade mechanism is simple: you buy, for example, 1 Euro for $ 1.2 and wait until the Euro rises to 1.3 dollars. Once this happens, you sell the Euro and get a profit of $0.1.
